ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2003-2004
PrecisAppointment of LOUIS GUAY as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Equatorial Guinea, with residence in Libreville; BRUCE JUTZI as Ambassador of Canada to the Slovak Republic, with residence in Prague; RANDOLPH MANK as Ambassador of Canada to the Democratic Republic of Timor-Leste, with residence in Jakarta; SANDELLE SCRIMSHAW as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Namibia, with residence in Pretoria; CLAUDIO VALLE as High Commissioner for Canada to the Commonwealth of the Bahamas, with residence in Kingston; and CHRISTOPHER WESTDAL as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Armenia and the Republic of Uzbekistan, with residence in Moscow.
